raw_text = "~ start
## 9am
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Mabel: Morningg babe 🥱
Mabel: img: mabel/196
Player: Morning Mabes
Player: Sleep okay?
Mabel: Mmm... kind of? 😅
Mabel: The noises came back late last night but... I tried my best to sleep
if Story.has_flag(\"LOVE\"):
	Mabel: Oh! That Sorority thing is literally TOMORROW night
	Mabel: And I think I have the jitters 😰
	Mabel: The other girls don't really know much either
	Mabel: Oh oh, apparently there's a pear thing too?
	Player: Pear?
	Mabel: Yup
	Mabel: One of the girls said so, though I'm not sure what that means lol
	Mabel: Pears 🍐
	Player: 🍐
	Mabel: They said they'd give me something to wear that's perfect for the occasion
	Mabel: So I'm kinda nervous 😆 I've seen how some of them dress lol
	Mabel: But all the girls wear them so it's gotta be normal, riiight??
	Mabel: Besides... do you like seeing me in Sorority style clothes? 😳
	Player: Example?
	Mabel: I know you know what they are babe 🙄 Silly duck
	Player: 😇
	Mabel: 😵
	- I do
		Player: I do
		Mabel: Really?
		Mabel: I guess I could try a little extra for you 😣
	- I don't
		Player: I don't
		Player: I prefer my version of Mabel
		Mabel: Hehe I knew it ☺️
		Mabel: Your version of Mabel is the only real one
	Mabel: I just really really wish you could be there with me babe 🥺
	Mabel: I'd feel better with you around
	Player: I wish I could too
	Mabel: Dumb one invite rule 😔
	Mabel: I'll just have to report back to HQ after the event 🫡
	Player: Roger!
	Mabel: Thought: Hopefully it'll be a totally normal event huh...
	Mabel: Thought: Somehow I doubt it
	Mabel: It's just a lil event though right? 😊
if Story.has_flag(\"LUST\"):
	Mabel: I think I slept just okay...
	Mabel: Thought: Every time I closed my eyes I was right back on that walk
	Mabel: Thought: My butt felt a bit
	Mabel: PinkThought: Tight... and his hands...
	do heart(1)
	Player: Maybe miss class and catch up with sleep?
	Mabel: Noo I couldn't do that babe!
	Mabel: I'm doing well in class, I don't want to lose momentum
	Mabel: I'll be fine! I'm just being a little dramatic hehe
	Mabel: Cause I like when you worry about me
	Mabel: Thought: I can NOT tell him some random guy walked me home
	Player: If that's how it is then okay
	Mabel: Mhm!! That's all it is 👍
	Mabel: Thought: ...I feel so icky lying to him
	Mabel: Thought: But I'm sure babe has a lot on his hands!
	Mabel: Thought: And I won't let it happen again
	do heart(0)
	Mabel: Thought: He's got my Social though... and it STILL won't let me block him
	Mabel: Thought: What if he's just... waiting after class again tonight
	Mabel: PinkThought: ...and if he is, what am I going to do?
Mabel: Anywhoo
Mabel: I really gotta ready up for classes
Mabel: Now to battle with the closet 😆
- Can I pick your outfit today?
	Player: Can I pick your outfit today?
	if Story.has_flag(\"LOVE\")
		Mabel: Ooh you remembered 🥰
	Mabel: I was thinking of wearing something simple today buuut
	Mabel: How abouuut...
	Mabel: You take me out on a date on the weekend and I let you pick my date outfit? 🥰
	- Deal! [#pinkheart]
		set Story.pink_heart += 1
		set Story.flag = \"Date4\"
		Player: Deal!
		Mabel: Eee yay, it's a date then! 🥰
		Mabel: I'll wear whatever you pick out for me hehe
		Mabel: Thought: A whole day with babe...
		Mabel: PinkThought: Finally... A break
	- I can't. Have Work!
		Player: I can't. Have Work!
		Mabel: Aww boo 🥺
		Mabel: That's okay!
		Mabel: Hard working babe is kinda attractive anyway
		Mabel: Rain check on that date though? Pinky promise?
		Player: Pinky promise
		Mabel: Yay 🥰 I'm holding you to it!
- What are you going to wear?
	Player: What are you going to wear?
	Mabel: Hmm something comfy, my brain's too fried to be fancy today 😅
	Mabel: img: mabel/197
	Mabel: This okay? 🥰
	Player: Cute!!
	Mabel: Yay hehe 😊
Player: Take care then babe!
Mabel: Wish me luck babe!
Player: You got this Mabes 😉
Mabel: Talk later! 🩷
if Story.has_flag(\"LUST\"):
	do social_post(\"mabel_presentation\")
=> END
"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
